metadata.name: Complex
metadata.description:
Complex (datasets) lives along its genesis counterpart Primitive (datasets) as the artist's manifesto. The genesis pieces stand alone as the natural beginning and end of the artist's future work, encompassing all that will be achieved in between. 

The parameters for this investigation can only be defined by their lack thereof, resulting in a piece that is defined by its own lack of definition, where the subject lives in the negative space, outside of the frame. This is a dynamic work that will follow the artist's journey, with a constantly evolving animation that will transform the piece over time.

2022
